C
x \in \mathbb{R}^n
h \in \mathbb{R}^n
Df(x).h = \lim_{t \to 0} \frac{f(x+th) - f(x)}{t}
\| f(x +th) - f(x) \| \le C \|th \| = C  |t| \|h\|
\|Df(x).h \| \le C \|h \|
